SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT Count(WhsCode) FROM OWHS WHERE WhsName like '%:1%' AND (BalInvntAc = ':2' OR SaleCostAc = ':2' OR ExpensesAc = ':2' OR RevenuesAc = ':2' or ':2' = '' or ':2' is null)

select WhsCode, WhsName,BPLid,BalInvntAc,SaleCostAc,RevenuesAc,ExpensesAc from OWHS where (WhsName like '%'+':1'+'%') AND ( (BalInvntAc = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') OR (SaleCostAc = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') OR (RevenuesAc = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') OR (ExpensesAc = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') )
